goodbrowserbadbrowser is a very simple browser detection script that powers the amazing good browser advocacy site: http://goodbrowserbadbrowser.com

our plan is to one day provide unobtrusive browser detection badges that you can display on your site to encourage upgrades to good browsers. rock out.

=== installation ===

get sinatra: http://github.com/bmizerany/sinatra/tree/master
run sinatra on edge as described in that file.

